'''鄒幸彤'''（{{lang-en|Tonyee Chow Hang-tung}}，{{bd|1985年|1月24日}}<ref>{{cite news |author1=BBC |title=香港「支聯會」鄒幸彤：不能用「紅線」替代「底線」 |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-57341764 |accessdate=2021-06-04 |date=2021-06-04 |archive-date=2021-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605211924/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-57341764 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210606/mobile/bkn-20210606173853532-0606_00822_001.html |title=政Whats噏：鄒幸彤「呼冤」　話大家將佢寫老晒 |website=on.cc |date=2021-06-06 |access-date=2021-06-13 |archive-date=2021-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210613133218/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210606/mobile/bkn-20210606173853532-0606_00822_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>），[[香港|香港]][[大律師|大律師]]，前[[支聯會|支聯會]]副主席。
鄒幸彤在香港出生和接受教育，祖籍廣東省茂名市.

== 生平 ==
鄒幸彤是[[香港|香港]]本地人，先後就讀[[蘇浙小學|蘇浙小學]]和[[英華女學校|英華女學校]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ywgsaa.org.hk/sites/default/files/newsletter/0310.pdf |title=英華女學校校友會通訊 2003年10月號 |format=PDF |access-date=2021-01-28 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208072653/http://www.ywgsaa.org.hk/sites/default/files/newsletter/0310.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。自小的興趣是行山，覺得行山很好玩；中學選修時決定報讀[[物理|物理]]科。中學時期成績優異，在[[香港高級程度會考|香港高級程度會考]]更考獲「5A」的成績<ref>{{cite news |author1=星島日報 |title=【六四 32 周年】香港支聯會副主席鄒幸彤被捕 涉宣傳未經批准集結 |url=https://www.singtao.ca/4980384/2021-06-03/news-%E3%80%90%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B+32+%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95++%E6%B6%89%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E6%9C%AA%E7%B6%93%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90/?variant=zh-hk |accessdate=2021-06-05 |date=2021-06-03 |archive-date=2021-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605081927/https://www.singtao.ca/4980384/2021-06-03/news-%E3%80%90%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B+32+%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95++%E6%B6%89%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E6%9C%AA%E7%B6%93%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90/?variant=zh-hk |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後在老師的推薦下報讀[[英國|英國]][[劍橋大學|劍橋大學]]物理學系，最後成功入讀。<ref>{{cite news |publisher=852郵報 |title=鄒幸彤：劍橋令我唔需要否定中國 |author=方浩文 |url=https://www.post852.com/164214/%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4%EF%BC%9A%E5%8A%8D%E6%A9%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/ |accessdate=2021-01-16 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129022828/https://www.post852.com/164214/%e9%84%92%e5%b9%b8%e5%bd%a4%ef%bc%9a%e5%8a%8d%e6%a9%8b%e4%bb%a4%e6%88%91%e5%94%94%e9%9c%80%e8%a6%81%e5%90%a6%e5%ae%9a%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

讀博士時發生[[汶川大地震|汶川大地震]]，同學知道後都很興奮，因為可以提供大量可研究材料，唯獨鄒一人放籌款箱支持災民。此事令鄒開始懷疑自己是否要「沿著此路繼續走下去」。加上大學時期也有參與義工工作，發覺[[人權事務|人權事務]]才是她的興趣所在；所以最後她毅然放棄博士學位，回流香港。有人替她不值，認為她前功盡廢；鄒表示「不是自己想做的，就無謂再花時間」。<ref>{{cite news |publisher=立場新聞 |title=縱機緣巧合　但無悔初心 ─ 訪80後支聯副主席鄒幸彤 |url=https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B8%B1%E6%A9%9F%E7%B7%A3%E5%B7%A7%E5%90%88-%E4%BD%86%E7%84%A1%E6%82%94%E5%88%9D%E5%BF%83-%E8%A8%AA80%E5%BE%8C%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4/ |accessdate=2021-01-16 |date=2016-01-19 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123014702/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B8%B1%E6%A9%9F%E7%B7%A3%E5%B7%A7%E5%90%88-%E4%BD%86%E7%84%A1%E6%82%94%E5%88%9D%E5%BF%83-%E8%A8%AA80%E5%BE%8C%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

回到香港後入讀[[香港大學專業進修學院|香港大學專業進修學院]]法律系，成功畢業，成為一名大律師，曾處理[[郭永健|郭永健]]港鐵示威案件、[[馮敬恩|馮敬恩]]圍堵港大校委會案件等等訴訟案件。2010年加入[[支聯會|支聯會]]做義工，六年後擔任副主席。<ref>{{cite news |publisher=眾新聞 |title=支聯會33歲副主席鄒幸彤：與年輕人割裂是死結，想不到辦法解決 |url=https://www.hkcnews.com/article/12333/%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4-%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B29%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-12333/%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%8333%E6%AD%B2%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4%EF%BC%9A%E8%88%87%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%89%B2%E8%A3%82%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%BB%E7%B5%90%EF%BC%8C%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E8%BE%A6%E6%B3%95%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA |accessdate=2021-01-16 |date=2018-05-28 |archive-date=2021-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121021903/https://www.hkcnews.com/article/12333/%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4-%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B29%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-12333/%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%8333%E6%AD%B2%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4%EF%BC%9A%E8%88%87%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%89%B2%E8%A3%82%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%BB%E7%B5%90%EF%BC%8C%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E8%BE%A6%E6%B3%95%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2021年12月4日獲[[中國民主教育基金會|中國民主教育基金會]]（Chinese Democracy Education Foundation，简称 CDEF）頒發的第35屆傑出民主人士獎<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F%E6%A3%80%E7%B4%A2/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F/20211206-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%B0%91%E8%BF%90%E4%B8%80%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%8D%E5%80%92%E7%9A%84%E6%97%97%E5%B8%9C-%E6%97%A7%E9%87%91%E5%B1%B1-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E4%BC%9A-35%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4 | title = 中国民运一面不倒的旗帜——旧金山“中国民主教育基金会”35周年 | publisher = RFI | date = 2021-12-06 | accessdate = 2022-01-02 | archive-date = 2021-12-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211216073548/https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F%E6%A3%80%E7%B4%A2/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F/20211206-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%B0%91%E8%BF%90%E4%B8%80%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%8D%E5%80%92%E7%9A%84%E6%97%97%E5%B8%9C-%E6%97%A7%E9%87%91%E5%B1%B1-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E4%BC%9A-35%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，12月10日獲得[[獨立中文筆會|獨立中文筆會]][[:Category:独立中文笔会林昭纪念奖得主|林昭紀念獎]]<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.chinesepen.org/blog/archives/160366 | title = 独立中文笔会授予邹幸彤2021年度林昭纪念奖| publisher = ICPC| date = 2021-12-10 | accessdate = 2021-12-11 | archive-date = 2021-12-11 | archive-url =  https://www.chinesepen.org/blog/archives/160366| dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 被警方拘捕 ===
2021年6月3日，香港警方以疫情為由，二度反對[[支聯會|支聯會]]於[[維園|維園]]舉行六四悼念晚會；而鄒表示會以個人名義到場。<ref>{{cite news |author1=RTHK |title=據了解支聯會副主席鄒幸彤被警方拘捕 |url=https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1594216-20210604.htm |accessdate=2021-06-04 |date=2021-06-04 |archive-date=2021-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210604112507/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1594216-20210604.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>翌日，她被警方以「涉嫌宣傳未經批准集結」為由拘捕。她被拘捕後向親友表示，要是未能參加集會，便會絕食一天。<ref>{{cite news |author1=蘋果日報 |title=六四32︱支聯會副主席鄒幸彤涉宣傳或公佈未經批准集結被捕 「若今天無法點起燭光 我將禁食一天」 |url=https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210604/PR56FWFURVDCFNIQOWXBQB3VDA/ |accessdate=2021-06-04 |date=2021-06-04 |archive-date=2021-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210621171343/https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210604/PR56FWFURVDCFNIQOWXBQB3VDA/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

之後她曾被保釋侯審；但在七一前夕，警方撤消鄒幸彤的保釋。<ref>{{cite news |author1=東網 |title=支聯會副主席鄒幸彤被控煽惑未經批准集結　周五提堂 |url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210630/bkn-20210630184311888-0630_00822_001.html |accessdate=2021-07-17 |date=2021-06-30 |archive-date=2021-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210717085401/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210630/bkn-20210630184311888-0630_00822_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>雖然她於再次被捕後曾經申請保釋，可是被拒絕。在法官書記問她是否明白罪名時，更大喊「悼念六四無罪」。<ref>{{cite news |author1=明報 |title=鄒幸彤涉煽惑集結提堂被拒保釋　鄒幸彤庭上稱「悼念六四無罪」【短片】 (16:31) |url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210702/s00001/1625207733375/%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4%E6%B6%89%E7%85%BD%E6%83%91%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B-%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4%E5%BA%AD%E4%B8%8A%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E7%84%A1%E7%BD%AA%E3%80%8D%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91 |accessdate=2021-07-17 |date=2021-07-02 |archive-date=2021-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211229125500/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210702/s00001/1625207733375/%e9%84%92%e5%b9%b8%e5%bd%a4%e6%b6%89%e7%85%bd%e6%83%91%e9%9b%86%e7%b5%90%e6%8f%90%e5%a0%82%e8%a2%ab%e6%8b%92%e4%bf%9d%e9%87%8b-%e9%84%92%e5%b9%b8%e5%bd%a4%e5%ba%ad%e4%b8%8a%e7%a8%b1%e3%80%8c%e6%82%bc%e5%bf%b5%e5%85%ad%e5%9b%9b%e7%84%a1%e7%bd%aa%e3%80%8d%e3%80%90%e7%9f%ad%e7%89%87%e3%80%91 |dead-url=no }}</ref>8月5日，邹幸彤获得保释候审<ref>{{cite news |title=港府撤告歌手黄耀明 邹幸彤获保释候审 |url=https://m.dw.com/zh/%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%92%A4%E5%91%8A%E6%AD%8C%E6%89%8B%E9%BB%84%E8%80%80%E6%98%8E-%E9%82%B9%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4%E8%8E%B7%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8A%E5%80%99%E5%AE%A1/a-58775944 |accessdate=2021-08-07 |archive-date=2022-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220102150525/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%92%A4%E5%91%8A%E6%AD%8C%E6%89%8B%E9%BB%84%E8%80%80%E6%98%8E-%E9%82%B9%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4%E8%8E%B7%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8A%E5%80%99%E5%AE%A1/a-58775944 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月8日，因拒绝在限期内向香港国安处提交运作资料，被警方上门拘捕<ref>{{cite web |title=【持續更新】支聯會拒交資料 多名常委清晨被捕 鄒幸彤FB直擊警登門 |url=https://www.hkcnews.com/article/45167/%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-45190/%E3%80%90%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E3%80%91%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E6%8B%92%E4%BA%A4%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E5%B8%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%B8%85%E6%99%A8%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4fb%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A%E8%AD%A6%E7%99%BB%E9%96%80 |website=眾新聞 |accessdate=2021-09-08 |date=2021-09-08 |archive-date=2021-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210908102233/https://www.hkcnews.com/article/45167/%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-45190/%E3%80%90%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E3%80%91%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E6%8B%92%E4%BA%A4%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E5%B8%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%B8%85%E6%99%A8%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E9%84%92%E5%B9%B8%E5%BD%A4fb%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A%E8%AD%A6%E7%99%BB%E9%96%80 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月9日警方對鄒幸彤的指控改為「[[煽動顛覆國家政權|煽動顛覆國家政權]]」，並正式起訴支聯會主席李卓人、副主席何俊仁和鄒幸彤，以及支聯會「煽動顛覆國家政權罪」。

